name: Panda
description: Meet Panda! He is a sweet cat who loves to snuggle and play with mice.

name: Musci
description: Musci is about 5 years old. He is a character who will bring a smile to your face. He is very playful and vocal.

name: Luna
description: Luna is a playful little kitten! She loves other cats and even gets along great with dogs!

name: Peaches
description: Peaches is a little older, but you wouldn't know it based on her energy levels. She loves to run and then take long naps in the sun.

name: Smokey
description: Smokey is a little shy at first, but once he gets to know you - he won't leave your side. He would do better in a household without small children
